data.description: Location, location, location this home is in one of the fastest growing parts of Lehigh Acres conveniently located down the road from State Rd 80 allowing you quick access to Fort Myers, Alva and Labelle Florida. Home features 3 bedrooms 2 bathrooms with den and open split floor plan. Once you make your way from the long driveway (that can easily park 6 cars)  and through the front door you will be greeted by an open formal dining room and your new den/study. Once past the study and formal dining area you'll find your self in your new huge kitchen over looking large living room and nook area making this the perfect home for entertaining friends and family. The split floor plan is perfect for keeping the kiddos on the other side of the home making for relaxing nights once settled in from a hard days work. I can keep going on and on don't take my word for it call your realtor and schedule your private showing today!!!
